TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select 'T' txt_key_string, sum(in_etl_control.record_count) txt_file_name, sum(in_etl_control.total_amount) txt_key_value, null dec_enforce_flg, null dte_update_date, null dec_running_flg from (select nvl(case when inctrl.txt_key_string = 'PAYMENT_RECORD_COUNT_LBC' then inctrl.txt_key_value end, 0) record_count, nvl(case when inctrl.txt_key_string = 'PAYMENT_TOTAL_AMOUNT_LBC' then inctrl.txt_key_value end, 0) total_amount from in_etl_control inctrl where inctrl.txt_key_string in ('PAYMENT_RECORD_COUNT_LBC','PAYMENT_TOTAL_AMOUNT_LBC') and inctrl.txt_file_name = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT') in_etl_control

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PERIOD_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT, DECODE(GFV.NEW_BUSINESSUNITMAP, 64, 'SGPAFA', OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT) TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, DECODE(GFV.NEW_POSITIONSEQ, NULL, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_POSITIONSEQ, GFV.NEW_POSITIONSEQ) as DEC_POSITIONSEQ, DECODE(GFV.NEW_PAYEESEQ, NULL, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ, GFV.NEW_PAYEESEQ) as DEC_PAYEESEQ, DECODE(GFV.NEW_POSITIONNAME, NULL, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_POSITION_NAME, GFV.NEW_POSITIONNAME) as TXT_POSITION_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENT_AMOUNT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_EARNING_GROUP, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_UPDATE, CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ, CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE, CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVEENDDATE, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE2, DECODE(CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3, NULL, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3) GENERICATTRIBUTE3, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE4, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE5, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE6, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE7, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE8, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICBOOLEAN2, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_TXN_DESCRIPTION, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_AGENT_STATUS, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_NRIC, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_BENEF_AMOUNT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_BANKCODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_BRANCHCODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNUMBER, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_ACCOUNTNAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_COMPANY_CODE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_RECIPIENT_ADDRESS FROM OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL inner join CS_PARTICIPANT CS_PARTICIPANT on CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ = OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ AND CS_PARTICIPANT.REMOVEDATE > SYSDATE inner join IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLEDATE on CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE <= TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE = TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') inner join IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLETYPE on OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE = IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_VALUE AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_PAYMENT_CYCLE_TYPE' AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_FILE_NAME = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' left outer join VW_OUT_GL_FA_ORI_AGENT GFV on OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT = GFV.PROCESSINGUNITNAME AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_POSITION_NAME = GFV.ORI_POSITIONNAME AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_POSITIONSEQ = GFV.ORI_POSITIONSEQ WHERE ((OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Settlment_Way = 'LBC' AND NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Agent_Status, '00') <> '70') OR (NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BENEF_SETTLMENT_WAY, 'UNPAID') = 'LBC' AND NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Agent_Status, '00') = '70')) AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND DECODE(GFV.NEW_BUSINESSUNITMAP, 64, 'SGPAFA', OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT) in ($$STR_BUSINESS_UNIT) AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ NOT IN (SELECT DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ FROM OUT_PAYMENT_RESULT_TRACE WHERE TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE') AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.txt_Remarks is null
